have come up and a simple human starts looking at it

00:00:55.080 --> 00:00:57.000
and he gets quite puzzled,

00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:59.000
“What sort of thing this world is?”

00:00:59.080 --> 00:01:02.000
It’s a very confused world, first of all.

00:01:02.280 --> 00:01:06.000
The confusion gives you a greater urge to seek,

00:01:08.080 --> 00:01:11.000
because you find, “What’s this going on?”

00:01:11.080 --> 00:01:14.280
Secondly, I went round your city today

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:17.080
