00:16:50.000 --> 00:16:53.000
Now in the medical science which I have done Myself

00:16:53.000 --> 00:16:55.000
is there’s only one type of human being.

00:16:55.160 --> 00:16:58.000
They do not separate one from another.

00:16:58.000 --> 00:17:02.000
But in everyday life you see we are so different from each other.

00:17:02.000 --> 00:17:05.000
So there are three types of people actually,

00:17:05.000 --> 00:17:08.000
one of them are the ones who are futuristic,

00:17:08.000 --> 00:17:11.000
another are the ones who live in the past

00:17:11.000 --> 00:17:13.080
and the others who are in the center.

00:17:13.280 --> 00:17:17.000
And they have three types of combinations then,

00:17:17.000 --> 00:17:20.000
that permutations and combinations work out with these,

00:17:20.000 --> 00:17:23.000
mainly, we should say, nine types of people.

00:17:23.000 --> 00:17:27.000
But then there can be even greater permutations and combinations

00:17:27.000 --> 00:17:31.160
depending on the kinds of people they meet, the kinds of people

00:17:33.000 --> 00:17:38.000
they admire or live with, or dominated with or dominate.

00:17:39.000 --> 00:17:43.000
So we have very complicated human beings in this world,

00:17:43.000 --> 00:17:47.000
doesn’t matter but they can brought down to the simple thing

00:17:47.000 --> 00:17:49.000
as left, right and center.

00:17:50.000 --> 00:17:53.160
If you can bring them down and classify them to these three things

00:17:54.000 --> 00:17:56.000
it’s very easy to treat them.

00:17:56.080 --> 00:17:59.000
Because if somebody is a right-sided person,

00:17:59.000 --> 00:18:02.000
he’ll have certain symptoms, he’ll be hot-tempered fellow,

00:18:02.000 --> 00:18:05.000
he’ll have a liver trouble. he’ll be thin,

00:18:05.000 --> 00:18:08.000
he’ll be shouting all the time on top of his voice.

00:18:08.000 --> 00:18:12.000
He may be good outside but in his family he would be very hot-tempered.

00:18:12.080 --> 00:18:15.000
He may be a person who is egoistical but maybe

00:18:15.000 --> 00:18:19.000
that he’ll look very humble because he has to deal with people

00:18:19.080 --> 00:18:23.000
and maybe that he may be very, very aggressive

00:18:23.000 --> 00:18:26.000
to such a point that he might become sadistic.

00:18:26.000 --> 00:18:30.000
Now the another type are the other ones who want always to run away,

00:18:30.000 --> 00:18:34.000
escape, they could be these, not people who will be grossly aggressive

00:18:34.080 --> 00:18:39.000
but will be very sly and will be trying all tricks and playing games

00:18:39.000 --> 00:18:41.080
and intrigues and all sorts of things

00:18:41.160 --> 00:18:45.000
and also, they will be living with their past, this type of thing.

00:18:45.080 --> 00:18:48.000
Now there are people who are in the center,

00:18:48.000 --> 00:18:51.000
the people who are moderate, who take life pleasantly,

00:18:51.000 --> 00:18:56.080
not bothered so much about life, life’s complications

00:18:56.080 --> 00:19:00.000
but keep above it. And they lead a very normal life,

00:19:00.000 --> 00:19:03.000
they do not indulge into any nonsensical things.

00:19:03.000 --> 00:19:06.000
These are the central type of people and that’s why

00:19:06.000 --> 00:19:11.000
all the religions came on this earth to establish that balance within.

00:19:11.000 --> 00:19:16.000
Religions, all of them came on this earth to establish that balance.

00:19:16.000 --> 00:19:19.080
Why the balance, again the question can come up, why the balance.

00:19:19.240 --> 00:19:22.000
The balance is for our ultimate ascent,

00:19:22.000 --> 00:19:28.000
for example, if you have to take an aero plane, ascend it,

00:19:28.000 --> 00:19:30.000
you have to first see if it is balanced or not,

00:19:30.000 --> 00:19:33.000
otherwise, it will be not floating horizontally

00:19:33.000 --> 00:19:38.000
but it might go one-sided, you see so one has to have a balance in life.

00:19:38.000 --> 00:19:43.000
But if you read yourself, if you face yourself you will understand that,

00:19:43.000 --> 00:19:46.000
“No, we are not so much balanced as we should have been.”

00:19:46.000 --> 00:19:50.000
So this balance has to be brought in, in human beings

00:19:50.000 --> 00:19:54.000
and that’s why we had great prophets on this earth

00:19:54.080 --> 00:19:56.000
to teach us the balance.

00:19:56.000 --> 00:20:00.000
And these prophets came at a time where we needed this balance,

00:20:00.160 --> 00:20:04.000
at every time people became imbalanced, they came on this earth

00:20:04.000 --> 00:20:06.000
to teach us balance.

00:20:06.000 --> 00:20:10.000
When this balance is lost, mostly we develop diseases.

00:20:10.000 --> 00:20:14.000
Even in religious things we can be very imbalanced.

00:20:14.000 --> 00:20:17.000
Like I’ve seen people reading Bible for three hours,

00:20:17.000 --> 00:20:19.000
what is the need to read Bible?

00:20:19.080 --> 00:20:22.000
I mean, for three hours you don’t learn anything.

00:20:22.000 --> 00:20:26.000
Actually, if you understand religion, is not to be read,

00:20:26.000 --> 00:20:29.000
but to be felt and experienced within yourself.

00:20:29.000 --> 00:20:33.000
Religion is like the ten valences of human beings.

00:20:34.000 --> 00:20:36.000
And the ten valences of the human beings

00:20:36.000 --> 00:20:39.000
when we lose the valence, we lose our balance.

00:20:39.160 --> 00:20:42.000
Now anything like, say a country

00:20:42.000 --> 00:20:44.000
which is over-developed loses its balance.

00:20:44.080 --> 00:20:47.000
A country which is under-developed also can lose its balance.

00:20:47.240 --> 00:20:49.080
Anywhere it can happen the same way,

00:20:49.280 --> 00:20:52.280
makes no difference whether you’re developed or under-developed,

00:20:53.000 --> 00:20:57.000
you are in the same way whether the balance is up or down,

00:20:57.000 --> 00:20:59.000
makes no difference. So it is like that.

00:21:00.000 --> 00:21:02.000
Now with the Kundalini what happens,

00:21:02.000 --> 00:21:05.000
the first thing it does is to create the balance within.

00:21:06.000 --> 00:21:11.000
When She rises in that part of the thing, area of the stomach

00:21:11.000 --> 00:21:14.000
it creates the balance, it brings forth the balance.

00:21:14.000 --> 00:21:19.000
Once the balance has come then it’s much easier for you

00:21:19.000 --> 00:21:22.160
to balance all the chakras which have gone upside down

00:21:23.000 --> 00:21:26.000
or which are crooked and the balance comes and fix them together.

00:21:27.000 --> 00:21:31.080
With that balance the chakras get their forms all right

00:21:31.280 --> 00:21:34.000
and because of that the Kundalini rises.

00:21:34.000 --> 00:21:38.000
She rises and pierces through your fontanelle bone area

00:21:38.000 --> 00:21:40.160
which is the true baptism.

00:21:41.000 --> 00:21:43.000
It’s not like somebody coming putting water onto your head

00:21:43.000 --> 00:21:45.160
and say, “Now you’re baptized.” And we accept it.

00:21:46.000 --> 00:21:50.000
It’s just an exercise, there’s no truth about it.

00:21:50.240 --> 00:21:55.000
The cool breeze of the Holy Ghost has to be felt on top of your head.

00:21:55.280 --> 00:22:01.000
So the truth has to be felt on your central nervous system,

00:22:01.000 --> 00:22:04.080
that means you must feel them on your fingertips.

00:22:05.000 --> 00:22:07.000
Mohamad Sahib has clearly said that

00:22:07.000 --> 00:22:11.000
at the time of Resurrection your hands will speak.

00:22:11.000 --> 00:22:13.000
But nobody wants to talk of Resurrection,

00:22:13.160 --> 00:22:17.000
nobody wants to talk of something that is good to happen,

00:22:17.000 --> 00:22:22.000
that there will be a period where people will be redeemed,

00:22:22.000 --> 00:22:25.000
that there will be a Redeemer, there will be a Counsellor;

00:22:25.000 --> 00:22:27.000
nobody wants to talk of that.

00:22:27.000 --> 00:22:30.080
They want to talk of the doomsday because people will be frightened

00:22:30.280 --> 00:22:33.000
and they’ll be pouring money for them.

00:22:33.000 --> 00:22:38.000
It’s a money-making fright which is created in people.

00:22:38.280 --> 00:22:42.080
The God Almighty who has created this beautiful universe

00:22:43.000 --> 00:22:46.000
has created you as special people who are human beings,

00:22:46.000 --> 00:22:53.000
do you think He’s going to allow us to destroy His great creation?

00:22:53.000 --> 00:22:56.000
He’s made us so beautifully within ourselves

00:22:56.000 --> 00:23:02.000
and we have to just understand that you’re not what you seem to be,

00:23:02.000 --> 00:23:06.160
you’re much greater, you’re much more, you are glorified by Him.

00:23:07.000 --> 00:23:10.280
Because only this thing has to happen and once it happens

00:23:11.000 --> 00:23:16.000
you’ll be surprised that you become in charge of yourself,

00:23:16.240 --> 00:23:20.160
that you become empowered with that power of God

00:23:21.000 --> 00:23:22.240
which flows through you.

00:23:23.000 --> 00:23:28.000
You can cure people, you can help people, you can raise Kundalini,

00:23:28.000 --> 00:23:31.000
you can get rid of all these stupid problems,

00:23:31.080 --> 00:23:35.080
all these big problems and all the universal problems

00:23:36.000 --> 00:23:38.000
because a transformation takes place within you.

00:23:39.080 --> 00:23:42.280
We had an alcoholic in Brighton one day,

00:23:43.000 --> 00:23:46.000
he came to the program completely drunk and he started abusing Me.

00:23:46.240 --> 00:23:51.000
I just smiled at him. Next day he came and he got his realization.

00:23:51.000 --> 00:23:54.000
Today he’s a first-class man, he’s earning such a lot of money,

00:23:54.080 --> 00:23:56.000
he’s doing so well.

00:23:56.000 --> 00:24:00.000
So what happens to you that you become yourself

00:24:00.000 --> 00:24:04.000
and to become yourself means you become the Spirit,

00:24:04.000 --> 00:24:08.000
and Spirit is the reflection of God within yourself.

00:24:08.000 --> 00:24:12.000
Once that happens, you become the dynamic power of God

00:24:12.000 --> 00:24:15.080
and you’re surprised the miraculous way you’re helped.

00:24:16.000 --> 00:24:19.080
Now of course, Sahaja Yoga has definitely cured cancer, no doubt,

00:24:20.000 --> 00:24:22.000
it can cure so many diseases.

00:24:22.000 --> 00:24:24.280
But when we wrote to the British council about it

00:24:25.000 --> 00:24:27.080
and they found out that we were curing people, they said,

00:24:28.000 --> 00:24:32.000
“There’s a big red tape going on,” they’ve to go through the files,

00:24:32.000 --> 00:24:34.000
they have to find out, this, that.

00:24:34.000 --> 00:24:38.000
So we said, “All right, doesn’t matter, let them have their own time.”

00:24:38.000 --> 00:24:41.000
But Sahaja Yoga is not only for physical being

00:24:41.160 --> 00:24:43.000
because you are not only physical being.

00:24:43.000 --> 00:24:46.000
I tell you there are many wrestlers and boxers

00:24:46.000 --> 00:24:49.240
who come to Me and say, “Mother,” who are very, very sturdy people,

00:24:50.000 --> 00:24:52.000
they say, “Mother, we have no peace, give us peace.”

00:24:52.240 --> 00:24:56.240
So it is not for physical being, it is not for mental being,

00:24:57.000 --> 00:25:01.000
it’s not for emotional being but it is for your spiritual being.

00:25:01.000 --> 00:25:05.000
But as you’re the temple of God, the temple has to be cleansed.

00:25:05.000 --> 00:25:08.000
When some guest is coming to your house, we clean the house,

00:25:08.080 --> 00:25:11.000
make it beautiful, put flowers, decorate it.

00:25:11.000 --> 00:25:15.160
In the same way, when your Spirit is going to enter into your attention

00:25:16.000 --> 00:25:19.000
your body has to be cleansed; your mind has to be purified

00:25:19.000 --> 00:25:24.240
and that you have to become a beautiful temple for that enlightenment.

00:25:25.000 --> 00:25:29.280
And that’s how as a by-product of this Kundalini awakening you get cured.

00:25:30.120 --> 00:25:32.200
Now what happens to your awareness,

00:25:32.200 --> 00:25:35.000
that you become collectively conscious.

00:25:35.000 --> 00:25:37.080
You become, again I say there’s no certificate.

00:25:37.080 --> 00:25:39.320
In Sahaja Yoga there’s no membership,

00:25:40.080 --> 00:25:43.080
of course you must have heard, there’s no money to be paid or anything.

00:25:43.120 --> 00:25:45.280
I mean, it is stupid, how can you pay money to God,

00:25:45.280 --> 00:25:47.160
what does He understand about money?

00:25:47.200 --> 00:25:50.080
How much money are you going to pay for yourself, first of all?

00:25:50.120 --> 00:25:53.080
He has given beautiful eyes to us, what do we pay Him, nothing;

00:25:53.080 --> 00:25:55.040
on the contrary we spoil them all the time

00:25:55.080 --> 00:25:58.280
by looking at things with lust and greed, we spoil them.

00:25:59.080 --> 00:26:02.240
We have adultery in our eyes, so we spoil them, the beautiful

00:26:02.280 --> 00:26:06.040
innocent eyes that He has given us, the pure eyes, we spoil them.

00:26:06.080 --> 00:26:09.280
But when you’re awakened, your eyes become so beautiful

00:26:09.320 --> 00:26:12.160
that you look at the person, the person gets all right.

00:26:13.280 --> 00:26:18.080
Your presence, merely your presence can help so many.

00:26:18.320 --> 00:26:21.000
But you have to achieve that state.

00:26:21.080 --> 00:26:25.120
Now as he said, you cannot demand it, you see, there’s no shop here.

00:26:25.240 --> 00:26:27.280
In a shop you pay the money so you can demand,

00:26:27.280 --> 00:26:30.200
“All right, come along, this was bad and I paid so much money.”

00:26:30.280 --> 00:26:35.280
But here what do you give? Your seeking, you’re seeking the higher being,

00:26:35.320 --> 00:26:38.080
you are not seeking your cure but you’re seeking

00:26:38.120 --> 00:26:40.040
the higher being within you.

00:26:40.080 --> 00:26:43.280
The property, the wealth of spirituality that resides in all of us.

00:26:44.040 --> 00:26:50.080
It is there, it is all there, only thing we have to pay attention to it and get it.

00:26:50.280 --> 00:26:53.280
Now you become collectively conscious means you start feeling

00:26:53.280 --> 00:26:56.080
other people on your fingertips.

00:26:56.240 --> 00:26:59.200
Even a child can say, “This is the problem, this is the problem,”

00:26:59.200 --> 00:27:02.080
now you have to just know what these denote

00:27:02.080 --> 00:27:05.080
and that’s what I have decoded that this means heart,

00:27:05.080 --> 00:27:08.080
this means something else, this means something else

00:27:08.080 --> 00:27:11.080
and all the centers, the five and the sixth and the seventh centers,

00:27:11.120 --> 00:27:13.000
on the left and the right-hand side.

00:27:13.080 --> 00:27:16.080
So immediately you’ll know the person’s suffering.

00:27:16.200 --> 00:27:20.040
But we don’t talk like doctors, we don’t say,

00:27:20.080 --> 00:27:22.120
“This fellow is egoistical,” not like that.

00:27:22.200 --> 00:27:24.320
But we’ll say, “His Agnya chakra in the front is catching,”

00:27:25.080 --> 00:27:27.240
that means he’s egoistical. But we don’t say that.

00:27:27.240 --> 00:27:30.080
Even a person will come and say, “Mother today my Agnya is catching,

00:27:30.120 --> 00:27:32.280
just take it out,” meaning, “I’ve been egoistical.”

00:27:33.120 --> 00:27:37.000
So the language is different as you must have read in the Bible

00:27:37.080 --> 00:27:39.280
that when they got their realization through the Holy Ghost

00:27:39.280 --> 00:27:42.040
they started speaking in strange languages.

00:27:42.080 --> 00:27:46.080
That doesn’t mean that they started speaking in Latin or Hebrew.

00:27:46.080 --> 00:27:51.080
It means that they started speaking in the languages of chakras,

00:27:51.160 --> 00:27:53.280
of centers, of the subtle centers.

00:27:54.040 --> 00:27:57.200
They started talking about the channels,

00:27:57.240 --> 00:28:00.280
because you become subtle, you start seeing something subtle.

00:28:00.320 --> 00:28:03.320
Like the way you see colors, animals do not see.

00:28:04.080 --> 00:28:07.080
The way you see filth and dirt the animals do not see.

00:28:07.160 --> 00:28:11.080
But when you become realized souls you see the dirt and filth of a

00:28:11.240 --> 00:28:17.000
much subtler nature. That is the sin that they call it or anything like that.

00:28:17.080 --> 00:28:19.080
So you become separated from this,

00:28:19.120 --> 00:28:22.160
and you start witnessing the whole world like a witness.

00:28:22.200 --> 00:28:26.120
You become collectively conscious, so supposing you get cured,

00:28:26.200 --> 00:28:31.080
so-called by Me, so-called, I would say, then there’s no obligation

00:28:31.080 --> 00:28:34.080
because if you’re part and parcel of Me, whom do I help?

00:28:34.160 --> 00:28:38.080
If this finger is paining and I rub it like this, whom do I help,

00:28:38.120 --> 00:28:40.080
I help Myself, isn’t it?

00:28:40.160 --> 00:28:42.320
So you become part and parcel of the whole

00:28:43.080 --> 00:28:45.080
and when you become part and parcel of the whole,

00:28:45.160 --> 00:28:48.160
the whole thing works out in such a homogenous way.

00:28:48.280 --> 00:28:51.200
As a result of that the people in England

00:28:51.240 --> 00:28:55.080
who were suffering from many diseases, people in Australia,

00:28:55.080 --> 00:28:57.040
so many countries now we have,

00:28:57.080 --> 00:29:01.200
most of the European countries we have tackled, have been cured.

00:29:03.120 --> 00:29:06.280
They have been cured of their diseases, of their ailments,

00:29:07.000 --> 00:29:09.240
they’ve become so powerful that they have no habits,

00:29:10.080 --> 00:29:13.240
nothing can deter them. They’re very joyous, happy people,

00:29:13.280 --> 00:29:17.000
if you see their photographs, you’ll say they’re lotuses sitting down

00:29:17.080 --> 00:29:21.040
beautifully pink. And the same thing is happening in India

00:29:21.080 --> 00:29:25.240
where I’m working for a much shorter time than I have worked in England.

00:29:26.000 --> 00:29:29.160
England has a special place; I must say because in the universe

00:29:29.200 --> 00:29:32.160
England is the heart of the universe.

00:29:33.120 --> 00:29:35.280
Perhaps you do not realize, you’re not aware of it.

00:29:36.080 --> 00:29:38.080
But English are very balanced people compared to

00:29:38.160 --> 00:29:41.280
all other Western people, I must say. But despite that

00:29:42.040 --> 00:29:44.280
sometimes you go off because you’ve lost your confidence,

00:29:45.080 --> 00:29:47.280
you try to follow French, you try to follow Americans,

00:29:48.000 --> 00:29:50.120
they have to follow you, not that you have to follow them.

00:29:51.000 --> 00:29:52.200
You can articulate.

00:29:52.280 --> 00:29:55.120
Now once upon a time it was the industrial development

00:29:55.160 --> 00:29:59.240
and all these things were there, so you articulated into these

00:30:00.080 --> 00:30:05.120
but now that is over. Now it has to be spiritual development,

00:30:05.240 --> 00:30:10.040
for that also I think one has to work out in England.

00:30:10.120 --> 00:30:13.160
And that’s how perhaps My husband got elected to this job

00:30:13.240 --> 00:30:16.160
and had to come to England. I’ve been here for ten years

00:30:16.200 --> 00:30:19.320
while in India I was just two years after I started My work.

00:30:20.080 --> 00:30:24.080
Of course I travel all over and the most wonderful thing I’ve found out

00:30:24.160 --> 00:30:29.160
about the Western people is that their hankering is no more now

00:30:29.200 --> 00:30:34.080
for material things. It looks little bit but is not so much.

00:30:34.200 --> 00:30:36.320
Once they get to their realization, they want to save others,

00:30:37.040 --> 00:30:38.200
they want to help others.

00:30:38.240 --> 00:30:42.160
Now all the way Dr. Warren has come from Australia.

00:30:42.280 --> 00:30:45.080
Now they said the psychology is such

00:30:45.080 --> 00:30:49.080
if the Australians talk to the English, they feel happy.

00:30:49.160 --> 00:30:54.160
So we sent English to America and you’ll be surprised that in Houston

00:30:54.240 --> 00:30:57.080
an Englishman went there and he was regarded as a very

00:30:57.080 --> 00:31:00.280
respectable man, you see, and they all listened to him nicely.

00:31:01.040 --> 00:31:05.320
It’s a funny psychology but we have great Sahaja Yogis even in England.

00:31:06.080 --> 00:31:10.200
In England we have very great people who have mastered this art

00:31:10.320 --> 00:31:14.120
and once you know this you become so scholarly

00:31:14.200 --> 00:31:15.200
that many a times

00:31:15.200 --> 00:31:17.080
these newspaper people ask Me,

00:31:17.120 --> 00:31:22.240
“Have you got all your disciples as scholars?”

00:31:23.080 --> 00:31:25.280
I said, “No, they’re not My disciples, they’re children.”

00:31:26.040 --> 00:31:29.280
But they become scholarly because they get to the essence of knowledge

00:31:30.000 --> 00:31:32.000
and this is the true knowledge.

00:31:32.080 --> 00:31:35.320
The otherwise whatever knowledge we have is of the dead.

00:31:36.080 --> 00:31:40.080
For example I was looking at your foundries, what do we do?

00:31:40.080 --> 00:31:43.040
We take out the dead and make something out of it.

00:31:44.320 --> 00:31:48.320
Can we make anything living? Can we transform these flowers into fruits?

00:31:49.080 --> 00:31:54.040
We cannot. After realization you start doing the living work

00:31:54.080 --> 00:31:59.240
and this is the process which a living work of living God.

00:32:00.080 --> 00:32:02.320
So you just cannot say that, “I stand on my head

00:32:03.080 --> 00:32:06.320
