(Question: There are many interpretations of the Bible,

00:52:27.080 --> 00:52:30.400
how do you know that your interpretation is the correct one?)

00:52:30.600 --> 00:52:32.600
Because it can be proved,

00:52:33.320 --> 00:52:36.280
it can be proved - you see the interpretations that

00:52:36.280 --> 00:52:39.600
come out of brains will be many -

00:52:40.240 --> 00:52:44.640
because it can be proved, you see now for example I say Christ resides

00:52:45.280 --> 00:52:47.640
on a center called as Agnya chakra

00:52:47.800 --> 00:52:50.440
which is placed on the optic chiasma

00:52:51.000 --> 00:52:54.240
which is controlling your pituitary and the pineal body,

00:52:54.320 --> 00:52:58.320
supposing I say that, all right? Now you keep your mind open about it.

00:52:58.480 --> 00:53:01.040
Now when I raise the Kundalini

00:53:01.760 --> 00:53:04.320
I find that it is stuck here.

00:53:04.440 --> 00:53:07.440
This is the window; this is the window of Christ.

00:53:07.760 --> 00:53:13.200
This is the blood of Christ, symbolic of His blood which protects you.

00:53:13.600 --> 00:53:15.680
Now this is the window of Christ.

00:53:16.080 --> 00:53:18.480
Now when I say that, this interpretation,

00:53:18.640 --> 00:53:23.000
that when the Kundalini is rising, it stops there.

00:53:23.200 --> 00:53:26.440
I have to take His name, request Him

00:53:26.800 --> 00:53:29.560
or I have to say Lord's Prayer.

00:53:30.000 --> 00:53:34.600
That's the mantra, that's the chanting one has to do, then it rises.

00:53:35.080 --> 00:53:40.320
He sucks in your ego and superego and you can see it clearly

00:53:40.400 --> 00:53:45.520
happening that here on the fontanel bone area, you get a soft bone

00:53:46.000 --> 00:53:48.480
and you see the cool breeze coming out of it.

00:53:48.720 --> 00:53:54.320
Now, you ask a question, putting your hands like this,

00:53:54.440 --> 00:53:58.560
ask a question, "Is this the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost?"

00:54:00.760 --> 00:54:03.640
The vibrations start flowing much more.

00:54:04.040 --> 00:54:08.440
Supposing you ask about somebody who is not a good man

00:54:08.600 --> 00:54:11.200
the burning may start coming on your fingers.

00:54:11.560 --> 00:54:14.400
Now supposing you say there is no God,

00:54:14.560 --> 00:54:17.080
you may get a terrible burning on your hands.

00:54:17.320 --> 00:54:21.400
So relatively you understand that whenever you ask for something

00:54:21.600 --> 00:54:24.480
truthful you get lot of vibrations.

00:54:25.480 --> 00:54:29.160
That means your computer has started working

00:54:29.360 --> 00:54:34.720
but for anything you find out whether it is true or not

00:54:35.000 --> 00:54:37.400
you have to work it out and see for yourself.

00:54:37.520 --> 00:54:42.200
Now when it happens with this if you get cured automatically,

00:54:42.720 --> 00:54:47.440
if you become a joyous personality, if you get completely transformed

00:54:47.680 --> 00:54:51.440
and you start curing others and you know all about it,

00:54:51.720 --> 00:54:53.720
you become knowledgeable about it. It’s not that

00:54:53.760 --> 00:54:57.280
you start shaking before someone and then the person gets…,

00:54:57.320 --> 00:55:02.080
you are quite normal and not only that you cure

00:55:02.200 --> 00:55:05.360
but you make another person so peaceful and joyful

00:55:05.560 --> 00:55:10.440
and enlighten that person that that person can himself give realization.

00:55:10.720 --> 00:55:13.720
You can see the Kundalini, the one that is in the triangular bone

00:55:13.800 --> 00:55:16.800
just like a heart pulsating in some people, not all,

00:55:17.080 --> 00:55:19.680
if there’s an obstruction in the higher chakra

00:55:19.760 --> 00:55:24.360
then you see it actually like that. We have got pictures of that.

00:55:25.720 --> 00:55:28.600
So whatever interpretation you give mentally is not true,

00:55:28.760 --> 00:55:34.760
you must prove it. So you have to accept it as a hypothesis.

00:55:35.480 --> 00:55:39.040
As in any science you give a hypothesis first

00:55:39.160 --> 00:55:40.520
and then try to prove it.

00:55:40.680 --> 00:55:44.480
If you have proved it then you have to accept it as a law

00:55:44.520 --> 00:55:49.080
otherwise you are dishonest. If you’re honest,

00:55:49.200 --> 00:55:52.120
really if you’re honest you have to accept it, isn’t it?

00:55:52.640 --> 00:55:55.000
That’s what My husband told Me that, “I cannot be anymore

00:55:55.080 --> 00:55:59.360
dishonest about it, I have to accept it, that’s the truth.”

00:56:02.200 --> 00:56:04.720
All right, now what’s the other question?

00:56:10.240 --> 00:56:13.760
(Warren: She’s heard and read that if you awaken Kundalini

00:56:14.040 --> 00:56:15.480
before it’s ready it can be dangerous.)

00:56:15.600 --> 00:56:19.560
Yes, must be, because the people who raise have no authority to do it;

00:56:20.240 --> 00:56:22.800
they don’t know how to do it. A person who is not a doctor

00:56:22.800 --> 00:56:25.720
if he tries to operate, what will happen? It’s dangerous.

00:56:26.200 --> 00:56:29.440
So far so many people their Kundalini has been awakened.

00:56:30.040 --> 00:56:32.080
I haven’t seen any dangerous things happen to anyone,

00:56:32.200 --> 00:56:34.280
on the contrary everybody has gained by it.

00:56:34.640 --> 00:56:36.480
The reason is you should know how to do it, you should be

00:56:36.520 --> 00:56:43.320
an authority to do it. Supposing you put one seed in the steel box,

00:56:43.720 --> 00:56:47.080
will it grow? No, you have to put it in the Mother Earth,

00:56:47.240 --> 00:56:51.080
she has the capacity to do it. In the same way the one who knows

00:56:51.200 --> 00:56:55.360
can do it, has to be an authority on it, and it is your Mother,

00:56:55.480 --> 00:56:59.000
She is your Mother. Everyone has an individual mother

00:56:59.040 --> 00:57:03.400
waiting to give that self-realization, how can She be unkind to you?

00:57:04.040 --> 00:57:07.680
Of course, in the beginning little heat is thrown out of your body

00:57:07.720 --> 00:57:10.480
because you’re heated up. It’s all right, doesn’t matter,

00:57:10.640 --> 00:57:14.560
it’s not so much and sometimes you do feel little shaking

00:57:14.720 --> 00:57:17.120
if you have been to a wrong type of a guru or something

00:57:17.280 --> 00:57:19.040
or if you are suffering from nervous trouble

00:57:19.120 --> 00:57:20.800
there’s a little shaking that's all.

00:57:21.400 --> 00:57:23.560
I have not seen anything wrong happening

00:57:23.680 --> 00:57:26.480
but like one gentleman came and sat on the ground. I said,

00:57:26.480 --> 00:57:29.400
“Why are you sitting on the ground like that with your feet towards me?”

00:57:29.560 --> 00:57:32.080
He said, “You know Mother, my Kundalini has been awakened

00:57:32.200 --> 00:57:36.280
and I’m jumping like a frog.” I said, “Why are you jumping like a frog?”

00:57:36.400 --> 00:57:39.280
He said, “My guru has said it and he wrote it down on a book

00:57:39.400 --> 00:57:43.000
that you jump like a frog.” I said, “Now are you going to become a frog

00:57:43.080 --> 00:57:50.040
or an earthworm?” Use your brains, all right?

00:57:50.760 --> 00:57:53.200
Nothing to be afraid of.

00:57:53.680 --> 00:57:56.480
I don’t think I look that frightful, do I?

00:57:59.760 --> 00:58:02.320
(Warren: If there are no more questions we’ll have the experience.)

00:58:02.680 --> 00:58:05.520
No, one more, yes let’s have it.

00:58:06.720 --> 00:58:09.160
Yes, please!

00:58:29.440 --> 00:58:31.000
It's a very long question.

00:59:11.600 --> 00:59:16.120
(Warren: First of all, she says that she agrees with everything

00:59:16.200 --> 00:59:19.160
that You’ve said, but she’s concerned about one thing,

00:59:19.320 --> 00:59:26.480
as she herself is a spiritualist medium, she is aware of the dangers

00:59:27.040 --> 00:59:31.120
and she wonders whether You are able to distinguish

00:59:31.160 --> 00:59:33.280
between the dangers and the blessings.)

00:59:33.520 --> 00:59:38.760
Absolutely, that’s what it is, that you should know what are the dangers.

00:59:39.000 --> 00:59:41.480
I’ve already told you, moving to the left and the right

00:59:41.640 --> 00:59:43.760
and the spiritualists are moving to the left.

00:59:44.080 --> 00:59:47.200
They’re using spirits and it’s very dangerous. You don’t know how

00:59:47.280 --> 00:59:51.320
to protect yourself, unless and until you get your realization

00:59:51.480 --> 00:59:54.320
you will not even know how spiritualism is wrong;

00:59:54.440 --> 00:59:56.800
absolutely it is most dangerous.

00:59:57.160 --> 01:00:01.440
There is no danger in Kundalini, but in spiritualism

01:00:01.520 --> 01:00:06.080
it’s most dangerous, whether you may be all right for the short time

01:00:06.280 --> 01:00:08.760
but they are spirits, you must know

01:00:09.080 --> 01:00:13.360
and spirits are the most dangerous things. Don’t go near them.

01:00:14.040 --> 01:00:15.480
It’s very surprising that in the West,

01:00:15.520 --> 01:00:17.480
people have no idea about spirits

01:00:17.600 --> 01:00:22.080
and the way they go headlong into it, it sometimes really upsets Me.

01:00:22.320 --> 01:00:26.400
In India people know about it, they call it Bhootavidya, Pretavidya,

01:00:26.440 --> 01:00:30.600
Smashanavidya, means the knowledge about the dead, we can say,

01:00:30.720 --> 01:00:34.720
in small the dead knowledge and they just don’t want to go near it.

01:00:35.120 --> 01:00:39.240
Say, the other day we had a visitor and I took her to a church

01:00:39.400 --> 01:00:41.720
and she was holding her sari, going like this. I said,

01:00:41.760 --> 01:00:43.720
“What’s the problem?” She said, “All dead are here,

01:00:43.720 --> 01:00:48.600
how can we cross over them?” She couldn’t understand

01:00:48.720 --> 01:00:52.080
and we have them in the churches where children go.

01:00:52.240 --> 01:00:56.160
It’s very dangerous. Only the realized people in India are buried,

01:00:56.320 --> 01:01:01.000
only realized souls are buried, not the people who are not realized.

01:01:01.280 --> 01:01:04.440
They’re not to be buried; they’re to be burned so that their body

01:01:04.480 --> 01:01:08.240
gets purified and again they come on this earth for their realization.

01:01:08.480 --> 01:01:11.360
And the dead in the church! It’s so dangerous,

01:01:11.400 --> 01:01:13.680
playing with spiritualists, nobody will do.

01:01:13.680 --> 01:01:18.200
Here I find housewives, and all people responsible

01:01:18.280 --> 01:01:20.760
getting into this mess of spiritualism.

01:01:21.320 --> 01:01:25.000
It’s all absolutely against Sahaja Yoga.

01:01:25.080 --> 01:01:28.680
We have nothing to do with them. On the contrary they suffer a lot.

01:01:29.080 --> 01:01:32.160
Spiritualists suffer a lot later on in life.

01:01:32.280 --> 01:01:36.280
Not only but seven generations of their family can suffer.

01:01:36.480 --> 01:01:40.080
We had a doctor here who came and I was surprised that

01:01:40.200 --> 01:01:43.040
he being a doctor was suffering from this kind of a disease.

01:01:43.080 --> 01:01:46.680
He was a Russian doctor and I asked him, “How did you get into it?”

01:01:47.240 --> 01:01:51.160
So he told me his mother, his grandmother had a hobby to take him

01:01:51.280 --> 01:01:54.480
to the cemetery. From his childhood he used to go to the cemetery.

01:01:54.520 --> 01:01:57.800
We could not locate the problem anywhere, he was very depressed

01:01:58.040 --> 01:02:02.320
and he used to get into problems and he had to give up his jobs.

01:02:02.480 --> 01:02:05.360
Now then we met another Indian doctor who was here

01:02:05.560 --> 01:02:10.120
and he had the same type of trouble, he’d given up his job and

01:02:10.320 --> 01:02:13.200
his wife didn’t know what to do and his children were also suffering.

01:02:13.320 --> 01:02:16.720
So I asked him a question, “Why, why you are like this?

01:02:17.080 --> 01:02:19.640
What did you do with your studies?” And he was quite normal.

01:02:19.680 --> 01:02:23.640
He said, “I led a very normal life.” But his grandfather used to do

01:02:23.720 --> 01:02:26.680
black magic, in the sense we call it, all this is black magic.

01:02:26.760 --> 01:02:31.200
All spiritualism is black magic, because it has to deal with the dead.

01:02:31.320 --> 01:02:34.280
And this boy was suffering, his children were suffering.

01:02:34.480 --> 01:02:37.080
Now we have one person from Guyana,

01:02:46.520 --> 01:02:48.360
another one from Guyana,

01:02:48.480 --> 01:02:53.400
he too, his father used to do this kind of a thing and he is suffering,

01:02:53.600 --> 01:02:56.680
he’s still suffering. He’s come to Sahaja Yoga and he’s still…

01:02:56.720 --> 01:02:59.120
but he can see now and he knows how to protect.

01:02:59.320 --> 01:03:05.480
So those who deal with dead are going to suffer, take it from me,

01:03:05.600 --> 01:03:08.720
whatever you may do, because they’re just like human beings

01:03:08.760 --> 01:03:10.720
and sometimes slyer people than we are.

01:03:11.120 --> 01:03:14.040
We should have nothing to do with the dead.

01:03:14.280 --> 01:03:17.600
Let them take their birth again, let them take their realization.

01:03:17.640 --> 01:03:20.600
All anorexia, all these diseases come out of that.

01:03:20.760 --> 01:03:24.120
So many diseases I’ve told you, cancer is caused by the dead.

01:03:24.320 --> 01:03:27.200
Be careful on that point and I don’t understand

01:03:27.240 --> 01:03:30.200
all educated people here, so much developed,

01:03:30.320 --> 01:03:32.600
how can you take…, Indians won’t take to it.

01:03:33.080 --> 01:03:35.760
They won’t go near it; they understand.

01:03:36.200 --> 01:03:40.200
Tantrikas and all that are prevalent only in very poor countries

01:03:40.440 --> 01:03:45.240
like… say, it’s a vicious circle, it brings poverty also. As soon as

01:03:45.280 --> 01:03:49.800
there is a dead in a family or a dead work done, the money disappears.

01:03:50.040 --> 01:03:53.440
The reason is the goddess of Lakshmi as we call them,

01:03:53.600 --> 01:03:57.000
she just disappears, she doesn’t like that black thing at all.

01:03:57.320 --> 01:04:00.800
And so the countries where we have, I mean, in our country

01:04:01.040 --> 01:04:04.080
the provinces which are poor, the whole country is not poor,

01:04:04.320 --> 01:04:09.480
they’re doing all black magic. In Kerala, it’s very poor country,

01:04:09.680 --> 01:04:12.720
I went there, they bury their dead in the house.

01:04:14.080 --> 01:04:16.720
It is all that. You must keep them out,

01:04:17.080 --> 01:04:20.800
because the goddess of wealth doesn’t like it.

01:04:21.560 --> 01:04:25.080
All this knowledge was not known to you but that doesn’t mean

01:04:25.200 --> 01:04:28.560
that you should go headlong into these things, it’s very, very dangerous.

01:04:28.720 --> 01:04:31.760
Never go near the dead; whatever it is the planet said,

01:04:32.040 --> 01:04:34.520
this, that, it’s all nonsensical.

01:04:35.200 --> 01:04:38.360
There’s no need to do that. But people are really…,

01:04:38.400 --> 01:04:41.080
I don’t understand, they’re daredevils.

01:04:41.280 --> 01:04:45.400
Like from America three big scientists came to see me,

01:04:45.520 --> 01:04:49.160
in India I’m very well-known. So they came to see me and said that,

01:04:49.240 --> 01:04:51.280
“Mother, teach us how to fly in the air.” I said,

01:04:51.360 --> 01:04:54.320
“Why do you want to fly in the air? What is the need?”

01:04:54.440 --> 01:04:57.400
“No, we want to leave our body and go to the moon.” I said,

01:04:57.440 --> 01:05:00.200
“You are already doing it with your body, why do you want to do it?”

01:05:00.320 --> 01:05:06.720
So they told me that, “Parapsychology is practiced now in Russia

01:05:06.720 --> 01:05:09.520
and we want to do the same.” I said, “It will affect them.”

01:05:09.720 --> 01:05:15.360
You see the way their presidents are killed, this is all parapsychology.

01:05:15.640 --> 01:05:19.080
I told them, “Don’t go near them.” They said, “No Mother,

01:05:19.080 --> 01:05:23.600
we want to do it.” I said, “But then you will be slaves of these dead,

01:05:23.600 --> 01:05:26.760
would you like to do that?” Still they said, “Yes we want to do it.”

01:05:27.200 --> 01:05:30.280
I said, “I have nothing to do but who has told you about this?”

01:05:30.440 --> 01:05:34.520
They said, “There is one fellow, Patanjali, who is a reporter.”

01:05:35.120 --> 01:05:38.600
I said, “Look at this Patanjali, he was suffering from this trouble,

01:05:38.760 --> 01:05:43.560
that his body used to be left behind and he would fly out and do…”

01:05:43.680 --> 01:05:46.680
And he came and his wife came and begged of me that

01:05:46.720 --> 01:05:49.440
they should be rid of this trouble and he’s telling them that

01:05:49.480 --> 01:05:52.200
am I going to put the trouble into them?

01:05:53.080 --> 01:05:56.000
All this parapsychology business, when I went first to America

01:05:56.040 --> 01:05:57.760
I must tell you, this experience is very good.

01:05:58.080 --> 01:06:01.480
I told them against parapsychology openly because they,

01:06:01.640 --> 01:06:04.560
I didn’t know what they were doing in parapsychology, first of all,

01:06:04.680 --> 01:06:08.760
and they are the people who invited me in their hall. I blasted them

01:06:09.280 --> 01:06:13.720
and I said, “Don’t do all this nonsense, it will all destroy you,

01:06:14.080 --> 01:06:15.520
just don’t go near them.”

01:06:16.120 --> 01:06:19.360
Second time when I went to America, only last year,

01:06:19.600 --> 01:06:22.520
I was giving on the television, I was on the television

01:06:22.600 --> 01:06:26.800
and before the television they had told that Mataji Nirmala Devi

01:06:26.800 --> 01:06:32.240
is going to come. And somebody telephoned from San Diego saying that,

01:06:32.320 --> 01:06:35.600
“Mother had come last time and she told us about parapsychology

01:06:35.640 --> 01:06:39.360
and she told us about the gurus, she warned us but we never listened

01:06:39.400 --> 01:06:44.480
to her and now we are destroyed people. Can she save us?” I said,

01:06:44.520 --> 01:06:49.280
“Yes, but still it’s difficult now, you should not have gone to that.”

01:06:50.280 --> 01:06:53.800
And the whole of that parapsychology thing is finished now.

01:06:54.320 --> 01:06:58.160
The building caught fire, the gentleman went to Australia,

01:06:58.200 --> 01:07:04.720
he got a funny temperament, he ended up in a lunatic asylum.

01:07:05.080 --> 01:07:10.320
The wife, she became paralytic, she ended up in a lunatic asylum.

01:07:12.760 --> 01:07:16.000
Brezhnev and all these people, they all suffered from this.

01:07:16.120 --> 01:07:19.520
You can see their faces, all like this, possessed.

01:07:20.160 --> 01:07:22.080
Don’t go near the spiritualists;

01:07:22.720 --> 01:07:25.680
don’t do that, it’s very dangerous, for you,

01:07:25.720 --> 01:07:28.480
for the progeny, for everyone. I must warn you;

01:07:28.560 --> 01:07:32.480
it’s the most dangerous thing and should not do that.

01:07:34.080 --> 01:07:36.120
Even if you don’t like it, I have to tell you.

01:07:36.240 --> 01:07:39.080
I don’t want to tell you something that’s not true.

01:07:39.400 --> 01:07:44.200
You depend on yourself, on your own Spirit, on your own being.

01:07:44.320 --> 01:07:48.040
Why to depend on somebody who’s dead, let them be alone.

01:07:59.040 --> 01:08:01.400
But when they suffer, they come to me, I’ve seen it,

01:08:01.720 --> 01:08:03.120
when they suffer then they come.

01:08:03.240 --> 01:08:06.400
Then it’s so difficult, you see, afterwards to give them

01:08:06.480 --> 01:08:09.160
realization, it’s so difficult, they’ve already harmed themselves.

01:08:09.320 --> 01:08:13.720
He (Warren) also had gone to someone like that, but his wife we lost

01:08:13.720 --> 01:08:17.600
because she was going too much of it; we’ve lost her, she’s…,

01:08:17.800 --> 01:08:22.080
I don’t know, she may come back, but I mean, she’s very much attacked,

01:08:22.200 --> 01:08:26.080
very much attacked. And she used to become like a furious personality

01:08:26.120 --> 01:08:30.400
and all sorts of things used to happen to her and I hope she comes back

01:08:30.480 --> 01:08:34.080
but it’s very difficult, you know, to pull them back out of the clutches

01:08:34.400 --> 01:08:36.480
of that, because they don’t know what they’re are doing,

01:08:36.480 --> 01:08:39.320
what they’re talking, how they’re behaving.

01:08:39.520 --> 01:08:45.040
A sickness of the worst type. Even AIDS is a sickness from the same.

01:08:46.240 --> 01:08:49.720
Most of the terminal diseases come from them.

01:08:51.120 --> 01:08:53.040
It’s very dangerous, don’t go near them.

01:08:53.200 --> 01:08:56.480
Christ has already told you; he’s the one who told so plainly,

01:08:56.640 --> 01:08:59.680
he took them out and put them in the pigs and pigs went into the sea.

01:08:59.800 --> 01:09:01.760
You have heard of that or not;

01:09:02.480 --> 01:09:06.520
so why do you want to bring them back? Put them in the pigs.

01:09:08.080 --> 01:09:12.480
If they don’t want to reside in the area where they are supposed

01:09:12.520 --> 01:09:13.920
to reside, let them go to pigs.

01:09:14.000 --> 01:09:16.360
They’ve no business… they’re busybodies, you know.

01:09:16.680 --> 01:09:20.720
There’re also one Dr. Lang in here. I must tell them about him,

01:09:20.800 --> 01:09:26.880
this Dr. Lang, late Dr. Lang, dead. And he capsized a man

01:09:27.240 --> 01:09:30.200
in Vietnam who was a soldier who was under a shock

01:09:30.400 --> 01:09:33.400
and this soldier came down to London

01:09:33.840 --> 01:09:36.720
to see his son and he said, “I’m Dr. Lang.”

01:09:37.280 --> 01:09:40.840
The son was shocked, he said, “Who? How are you… my father is dead.”

01:09:41.160 --> 01:09:44.240
He said, “No, your father has possessed me, and he has told me

01:09:44.320 --> 01:09:47.840
that I must start my clinic here and there are many doctors

01:09:47.880 --> 01:09:51.680
who want to help me and I’m going to start this clinic.”

01:09:52.280 --> 01:09:57.440
So the son listened to it and he said, “How am I to believe

01:09:57.520 --> 01:10:00.920
that you are my father?” Then he told him some secrets

01:10:01.120 --> 01:10:04.320
which were between the two, and told about the house

01:10:04.400 --> 01:10:06.840
where he had put some money and all that.

01:10:07.160 --> 01:10:09.280
And the son was surprised and he started the clinic;

01:10:09.440 --> 01:10:13.800
and that’s how the International Curative Centre of Late Dr. Lang

01:10:13.800 --> 01:10:19.320
started in London. How I came to know about it, that in 1974

01:10:19.400 --> 01:10:21.520
I met a lady, she was shaking all the time like this.

01:10:21.520 --> 01:10:23.200
I said, “What’s this?”

01:10:23.360 --> 01:10:27.000
She said, “Mother, I don’t know but I was cured by Dr. Lang,

01:10:27.160 --> 01:10:30.760
late Dr. Lang.” Then she told me the story. But they were honest

01:10:30.880 --> 01:10:34.160
to tell about this whole thing what had happened but he did not enter

01:10:34.200 --> 01:10:37.760
into the body of the boy, his son, entered into somebody else

01:10:37.800 --> 01:10:40.640
who was a very healthy man. And she told me that,

01:10:40.680 --> 01:10:43.120
“When I wrote to them, I am suffering from these troubles,

01:10:43.160 --> 01:10:47.880
stomach trouble, they told me that you will have the experience

01:10:47.960 --> 01:10:52.040
at such and such exact this time.” That shows it’s not living

01:10:52.280 --> 01:10:55.800
because you cannot give time to something that is living. You cannot

01:10:55.840 --> 01:11:00.240
say exactly what time a flower is going to become the fruit, can you?

01:11:00.720 --> 01:11:04.320
And this thing entered into her body, she started shaking, shaking,

01:11:04.520 --> 01:11:06.520
and her stomach was all right.

01:11:06.680 --> 01:11:09.520
For about two years she was all right, afterwards the whole body

01:11:09.640 --> 01:11:11.880
started shaking, she became like a mad woman.

01:11:12.120 --> 01:11:15.600
She used to run out of the house and people would say that,

01:11:15.800 --> 01:11:20.240
“This woman is going to kill herself.” Once she jumped from

01:11:20.280 --> 01:11:23.760
a very high ceiling just to kill herself but somehow she was saved,

01:11:24.080 --> 01:11:29.160
and they brought her to Me and she told me the story of late Dr. Lang.

01:11:30.000 --> 01:11:33.480
So I have to tell you, though they cure you for a while,

01:11:33.480 --> 01:11:38.240
don’t go near them, better you cure yourself and know all about it.

01:11:38.560 --> 01:11:40.800
You be the master of yourself.

01:11:42.160 --> 01:11:45.080
It’s nice she brought out the point because otherwise…

01:11:45.360 --> 01:11:50.920
it’s all Sahaj, it’s spontaneous, so that I could tell you about it;

01:11:51.160 --> 01:11:55.400
it’s quite possible that people could take to that.

01:11:57.760 --> 01:12:00.600
Now should we have the experience now, all of us?
